  "instructions": [
    "Prepare the banana leaves by washing and drying them.",
    "In a large pan, heat the peanut butter over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped Mars bar and stir until melted and smooth.",
    "Add the honey and stir until well combined.",
    "Add the cooked rice, strawberries, coconut flakes, and pineapple chunks to the pan and stir-fry for 5 minutes.",
    "Spoon the stir-fry mixture onto the prepared banana leaves.",
    "Fold the banana leaves to form a packet and serve immediately.",
    "Garnish with additional coconut flakes and strawberries if desired."
